        "subject": "LU-2642 ldiskfs: handle ext4_ext_cache without ec_type member",
        "message": "LU-2642 ldiskfs: handle ext4_ext_cache without ec_type member\n\nCommit b05e6ae5 (v2.6.37) removed the ec_type member from struct\next4_ext_cache since it can be calculated using ->ec_len or\n->ec_start.\n\nWe introduce a shim to do the calculation if the member is missing.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: If51618a7cd9c9682689af619354d66b550947a1e\n"
